%20of%20Nepal.%20Their%20model%20is%20open-source%2C%20and%20they%20regularly%20train%20community%20leaders%2C%20educators%2C%20and%20volunteers.%20As%20more%20schools%20integrate%20bottle%20brick-making%20into%20their%20curriculum%2C%20a%20quiet%20yet%20profound%20environmental%20movement%20is%20taking%20shape%2C%20led%20not%20by%20corporations%20or%20governments%2C%20but%20by%20children%2C%20teachers%2C%20and%20everyday%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20not%20trying%20to%20change%20the%20world%20overnight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Momo%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20just%20helping%20people%20realise%20they%20already%20have%20the%20tools%20to%20make%20a%20difference.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20every%20bench%20built%2C%20every%20wall%20laid%2C%20and%20every%20child%20who%20gleefully%20stuffs%20a%20wrapper%20into%20a%20PET%20bottle%2C%20a%20new%20possibility%20unfolds%2C%20one%20where%20sustainability%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20abstract%20goal%2C%20but%20a%20tangible%2C%20touchable%20act%20of%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20quiet%20revolution%2C%20one%20bottle%20at%20a%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20heart%2C%20Green%20Ammo%E2%80%99s%20Bottle%20Brick%20movement%20is%20not%20about%20bricks%20or%20benches.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20belief.%20Belief%20that%20everyday%20people%2C%20especially%20young%20children%2C%20can%20drive%20extraordinary%20change.%20From%20school%20corridors%20in%20Meghalaya%20to%20remote%20hamlets%20in%20Himachal%20and%20border%20villages%20in%20Nepal%2C%20the%20initiative%20is%20igniting%20a%20quiet%20revolution.%20One%20where%20waste%20isn%E2%80%99t%20discarded%20but%20reimagined.%20One%20where%20classrooms%20aren%E2%80%99t%20confined%20to%20textbooks%20but%20built%2C%20quite%20literally%2C%20by%20the%20hands%20of%20children%20with%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D