%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fsustainable-architecture-1753275562-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475173%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Earth%20Centre%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20built%20using%20terracotta%20as%20the%20hero%20material%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Venkataramanan%20Associates%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETerracotta%20is%2C%20at%20its%20core%2C%20baked%20earth.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F361124%2Frammed-earth-timber-clay-sustainable-home-material-architecture-projects-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenergy-saving%20material%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20research%20suggests%2C%20elaborating%20that%20the%20firing%20process%20used%20in%20terracotta%20production%20typically%20requires%20lower%20temperatures%20compared%20to%20concrete%3B%20terracotta%20is%20also%20moisture-proof%3B%20it%20has%20good%20thermal%20and%20acoustic%20insulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20genius%20of%20the%20project%20lies%20in%20using%20terracotta%20not%20as%20a%20flat%20tile%20but%20as%20custom-moulded%20panels%20with%20a%20flared%20profile.%20This%20adds%20a%20bold%20dynamic%20to%20the%20construction.%20Elaborating%20on%20the%20design%2C%20Dhiraj%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CFifty%20percent%20of%20the%20terracotta%20used%20is%20recycled%2C%20making%20this%20one%20of%20the%20few%20buildings%20in%20Bengaluru%20to%20adopt%20such%20a%20high%20proportion%20of%20post-industrial%20terracotta.%20This%20porous%20terracotta%20screen%20contributes%20to%20a%20cooler%20microclimate%2C%20which%20is%20particularly%20important%20in%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20increasingly%20warm%20urban%20fabric.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%20that%20recycled%20terracotta%20has%20significantly%20lower%20embodied%20energy%20than%20freshly%20manufa