%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20sons%20had%20to%20take%20up%20odd%20jobs%20to%20support%20us.%20Now%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20finally%20seeing%20the%20rewards.%E2%80%9D%20His%20story%20echoes%20across%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20aren%E2%80%99t%20isolated%20successes%E2%80%94they%E2%80%99re%20part%20of%20a%20growing%20movement.%20With%20initiatives%20like%20JalTara%2C%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20Save%20Groundwater%20Foundation%20(SGF)%2C%20a%20new%20model%20of%20rural%20resilience%20is%20taking%20root.%20Affordable%2C%20scalable%20techniques%20like%20rainwater%20harvesting%20and%20aquifer%20recharge%20are%20helping%20reverse%20decades%20of%20water%20stress.%20As%20tanks%20dry%20up%20less%20often%20and%20livelihoods%20flourish%2C%20communities%20that%20once%20teetered%20on%20the%20edge%20are%20rediscovering%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20vision%20and%20impact%20of%20JalTara%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Purushottam%20Vayal%2C%20a%20former%20political%20science%20professor%20turned%20passionate%20water%20conservationist%2C%20recognised%20the%20devastating%20impact%20of%20recurring%20droughts%20on%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20farmers.%20Inspired%20by%20the%20philosophy%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EPani%20adhva%2C%20pani%20jirva%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(hold%20water%2C%20let%20it%20percolate)%2C%20he%20developed%20the%20JalTara%20grassroots%20movement%20to%20harness%20rainwater%20through%20innovative%20yet%20affordable%20methods%20such%20as%20soak%20pits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVayal%20began%20his%20experiment%20on%20his%2060-acre%20farm%2C%20constructing%20simple%20yet%20effective%20pits%20layered%20with%20stones%2C%20gravel%2C%20and%20sand%20to%20capture%20rainwater%20and%20recharge%20groundwater.%20The%20results%20were%20immediate%3A%20wells%20that%20once%20dried%20up%20by%20December%20now%20brim%20with%20water%2C%20fields%20became%20more%20fertile%2C%20and%20orchards%20flourished%20where%20there%20had%20once%20been%20barren%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20edge%20of%20my%20fields%20in%20Watur%20village%2C%20where%20rainwater%20used%20to%20collect%2C%20I%20began%20laying%20recharge%20pits%20in%20March%20and%20April.%20Every%20acre%20had%20one%20soak%20pit%2C%20so%20I%20installed%20six%20in%20total.%20When%20the%20rains%20arrived%20in%20June%202020%20and%20continued%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%2C%20I%20rushed%20to%20the%20fields%20the%20next%20morning%2C%20jumping%20from%20puddle%20to%20puddle%20with%20an%20umbrella%20in%20hand.%20I%20was%20overjoyed%20to%20see%20that%20the%20rainwater%20had%20percolated%20into%20the%20ground.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20998px)%20100vw%2C%20998px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-dugout-soka-pit_11zon-1753180220.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22998%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maharashtra%20JalTara%20groundwater%20recharge%20pits%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-dugout-soka-pit_11zon-1753180220.jpg%20998w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-dugout-soka-pit_11zon-1753180220-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-dugout-soka-pit_11zon-1753180220-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-dugout-soka-pit_11zon-1753180220-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-dugout-soka-pit_11zon-1753180220-150x112.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-474373%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22748%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWater%20awareness%20campaigns%20led%20to%20the%20deepening%20and%20widening%20of%20streams%2C%20drains%2C%20and%20rivers%20in%20Mantha%20and%20Partur%20talukas.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20began%20as%20a%20personal%20project%20soon%20grew%20into%20a%20regional%20phenomenon.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20selected%20four%20villages%E2%80%94Meskheda%2C%20Murumkhed%2C%20Taltondi%2C%20and%20Limbkheda%E2%80%94and%20laid%20recharge%20pits%20in%20May%202021.%20That%20year%2C%20none%20of%20these%20villages%20needed%20water%20tankers%20in%20December%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vayal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWater%20awareness%20campaigns%20led%20to%20the%20deepening%20and%20widening%20of%20streams%2C%20drains%2C%20and%20rivers%20in%20Mantha%20and%20Partur%20talukas%2C%20with%20Vayal%20at%20the%20forefront.%20Notably%2C%20in%202017%2C%20youth%20from%20ten%20villages%20were%20trained%20and%20subsequently%20revitalised%2085%20km%20of%20waterways%2C%20constructed%20dams%2C%20planted%20trees%2C%20and%20revived%20the%20Nangartas%20river%2C%20transforming%20these%20villages%20into%20water-rich%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20four%20years%20later%2C%20we%20found%20that%20the%20contour%20trenches%20we%20had%20dug%20were%20filled%20with%20silt%2C%20making%20them%20ineffective%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vayal%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20realised%20the%20limitations%20of%20traditional%20watershed%20schemes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAddressing%20the%20water%20crisis%20at%20its%20core%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332290%2Fmaharashtra-water-scarcity-drought-prone-jalna-district-gets-aid-water-bodies-desilted%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWater%20scarcity%20and%20drought%20remain%20the%20root%20causes%20of%20distress%20for%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20farmers.%20%3C%2Fa%3EOf%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%2044%2C000%20villages%2C%2028%2C000%20face%20water%20crises.%20Farmers%20often%20struggle%20to%20harvest%20even%20the%20Kharif%20crop%20and%20must%20anxiously%20await%20the%20Rabi%20season.%20Recognising%20this%2C%20Vayal%20envisioned%20a%20way%20to%20intercept%20wasted%20rainwater%20from%20fields%20through%20suction%20pits.%20This%20vision%20gave%20rise%20to%20the%20JalTara%20programme%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVayal%E2%80%99s%20idea%20took%20clearer%20shape%20through%20the%20influence%20of%20his%20friend%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.savegroundwater.org%2Fauthor%2Fmanu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Manu%20Nimbodhiri%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20NRI%20settled%20in%20the%20United%20States%20who%20visited%20Maharashtra.%20Their%20collaboration%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20an%20affordable%2C%20easily%20replicable%20technique%20suited%20for%20village%20settings%3A%20digging%204%C3%974%20feet%20wide%20and%20six%20to%20seven%20feet%20deep%20pits%2C%20layered%20with%20stones%2C%20gravel%2C%20and%20sand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20recharge%20pits%20allow%20rainwater%20to%20bypass%20the%20topsoil%20and%20percolate%20directly%20into%20the%20groundwater%20table.%20Put%20simply%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20establishing%20a%20dense%20network%20of%20small%20recharge%20pits%20at%20the%20lowest%20point%20of%20every%20acre%20of%20farmland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProven%20results%20and%20scalable%20solutions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRoughly%2064%25%20of%20all%20villages%20in%20Maharashtra%20are%20classified%20as%20water-scarce.%20Building%20dams%2C%20laying%20canals%2C%20or%20linking%20rivers%20are%20all%20time-%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341533%2Fdragon-fruit-farming-in-solapur-drought-maharashtra-mahesh-asabe-rukmini-farms-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecost-intensive%20solutions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20farmer-laid%20recharge%20pits%20are%20cost-effective%20and%20doable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vayal%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20this%20technique%20has%20been%20profound.%20Wells%20that%20previously%20dried%20up%20by%20December%20were%20half-filled%20after%20the%20first%20rain%20and%20overflowing%20after%20the%20second.%20Eroded%20land%20along%20streams%20became%20fertile%20within%20a%20year%2C%20with%20citrus%20orchards%20thriving%20where%20barrenness%20once%20prevailed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201248px)%20100vw%2C%201248px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-ready-soak-pit-Prof-Wayal-in-the-centre_11zon-1753180232.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221248%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maharashtra%20JalTara%20groundwater%20recharge%20pits%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-ready-soak-pit-Prof-Wayal-in-the-centre_11zon-1753180232.jpg%201248w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-ready-soak-pit-Prof-Wayal-in-the-centre_11zon-1753180232-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-ready-soak-pit-Prof-Wayal-in-the-centre_11zon-1753180232-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-ready-soak-pit-Prof-Wayal-in-the-centre_11zon-1753180232-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-ready-soak-pit-Prof-Wayal-in-the-centre_11zon-1753180232-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-474376%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22936%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Vayal%E2%80%99s%20idea%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20an%20affordable%2C%20easily%20replicable%20technique%20suited%20for%20village%20settings.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFunded%20by%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgroundwater.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Groundwater%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20few%20others%20from%20America%2C%20JalTara%20has%20impacted%20100%20villages%20in%20Mantha%2C%2050%20in%20Partur%2C%2020%20in%20Jalna%2C%20and%20two%20in%20Ghansangi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20its%20benefits%2C%20Vayal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFour%20months%20of%20rain%20seep%20into%20the%20ground%20through%20this%20pit%2C%20and%20the%20water%20level%20increases%20tremendously.%20The%20water%20that%20accumulates%20during%20heavy%20rains%20drains%20through%20the%20pit%2C%20and%20due%20to%20continuous%20water%20seeping%20for%20four%20months%2C%20moisture%20builds%20up%20in%20that%20one%20acre.%20From%20that%20moisture%2C%20microorganisms%20survive%20and%20produce%20micronutrients%2C%20which%20benefit%20crop%20yield.%20Interestingly%2C%20earlier%20disputes%20over%20flooded%20fields%20have%20significantly%20reduced.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20starting%20in%202022%2C%201%2C75%2C000%20soak%20pits%20have%20been%20laid%2C%20rejuvenating%20the%20water%20table%20and%20enabling%20farmers%20to%20sow%20timely%20Rabi%20crops%2C%20breaking%20the%20cycle%20of%20drought.%20As%20Vayal%20points%20out%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201248px)%20100vw%2C%201248px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-ready-soak-pit_11zon-1753180238.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221248%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maharashtra%20JalTara%20groundwater%20recharge%20pits%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-ready-soak-pit_11zon-1753180238.jpg%201248w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-ready-soak-pit_11zon-1753180238-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-ready-soak-pit_11zon-1753180238-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-ready-soak-pit_11zon-1753180238-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-ready-soak-pit_11zon-1753180238-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-474377%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22702%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%204%C3%974%20feet%20wide%20and%20six%20to%20seven%20feet%20deep%20pit%2C%20layered%20with%20stones%2C%20gravel%2C%20and%20sand.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDid%20you%20know%20that%20an%20acre%20of%20land%20receiving%20750%20mm%20of%20rain%20brings%20over%203%20million%20litres%20of%20water%3F%20If%20the%20recharge%20pits%20absorb%20even%2020%20to%2030%20percent%20of%20it%2C%20the%20amount%20is%20mind-boggling%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vayal%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20communities%20through%20education%20and%20action%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20critical%20component%20of%20JalTara%20is%20community%20education.%20Each%20project%20cycle%20includes%20four%20months%20of%20villager%20education%20and%20data%20gathering%2C%20followed%20by%20two%20months%20of%20mechanized%20pit%20digging%20before%20the%20monsoon.%20This%20ensures%20maximum%20impact%20during%20the%20rainy%20season%2C%20improving%20water%20conservation%20and%20reducing%20flood%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%E2%80%99s%20success%20is%20rooted%20in%20community%20participation.%20Farmers%20volunteer%20through%20%3Cem%3Eshramdaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(collective%20labour)%20to%20fill%20the%20pits%20and%20provide%20materials%20like%20sand%2C%20pebbles%2C%20and%20stones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pre-%20and%20post-project%20impact%20is%20rigorously%20analysed%20by%20geologists%20and%20experts%20from%20the%20Groundwater%20Foundation%2C%20using%20photos%2C%20geotags%2C%20and%20scientific%20measurements%20of%20the%20water%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D