p%3E%E2%80%9CNormally%2C%20making%20paper%20from%20wood%20pulp%20uses%20around%2060%25%20soda.%20But%20we%20found%20that%20with%20water%20hyacinth%2C%20you%20only%20need%20about%206%25.%20And%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20pulp%20was%20excellent%20%E2%80%94%20strong%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20easy%20to%20work%20with.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20breakthrough%20proved%20what%20she%20had%20long%20suspected%20%E2%80%94%20water%20hyacinth%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20be%20a%20burden.%20With%20the%20right%20technique%2C%20it%20could%20become%20a%20sustainable%2C%20scalable%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBack%20home%2C%20but%20not%20yet%20on%20board%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnergised%20by%20her%20success%20in%20Germany%2C%20Sushmita%20returned%20to%20India%20with%20a%20clear%20goal%20%E2%80%94%20to%20scale%20up%20the%20process%20and%20introduce%20water%20hyacinth%20paper%20into%20mainstream%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20began%20reaching%20out%20to%20paper%20industries%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20could%20be%20a%20new%20income%20source%20for%20communities%20that%20pulp%20water%20hyacinth%20and%20supply%20it%20to%20factories.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20quickly%20ran%20into%20a%20familiar%20roadblock%3A%20hesitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20data%20and%20lab%20results%2C%20paper%20manufacturers%20were%20reluctant%20to%20test%20alternative%20raw%20materials.%20Adopting%20a%20new%20process%20meant%20investment%2C%20trial%20runs%2C%20and%20regulatory%20approvals%20%E2%80%94%20and%20many%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20take%20the%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%